---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';

export const title = "Scarborough Dispensary Guide";
---

<Layout 
  title="Scarborough Dispensary Guide | Maine Dispensary Guide" 
  description="Complete guide to opening a cannabis dispensary in Scarborough, Maine. Market analysis, regulations, and investment requirements."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500916434205-0c77489c6cf7?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
>
  <article>
    <div class="article-header">
      <h1>Scarborough Dispensary Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">How to open a cannabis dispensary in Scarborough, Maine</p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Scarborough, one of Maine's fastest-growing communities with 20,000+ residents, is located just south of Portland along the coast. Known for its beaches, golf courses, and growing residential population, Scarborough offers cannabis entrepreneurs access to an affluent, growing market with significant tourism traffic. Before moving forward, familiarize yourself with the <a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-real-estate/">real estate requirements</a> essential for success.</p>
    </section>

    <Callout title="Scarborough: A Local Opportunity" type="passion">
      Operating in Scarborough is more than just a business; it's about becoming a pillar of the community. Focus on local engagement and education to build lasting trust with your neighbors.
    </Callout>


    <section>
      <h2>Why Scarborough?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Portland Adjacent</strong> - Minutes from Portland</li>
        <li><strong>Affluent Market</strong> - Higher income demographics</li>
        <li><strong>Tourism Traffic</strong> - Beach visitors in summer</li>
        <li><strong>Growing Population</strong> - Among fastest-growing in Maine</li>
        <li><strong>Good Visibility</strong> - I-95 runs through town</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Scarborough Market</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Factor</th><th>Assessment</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Population</td><td>20,000+</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Summer Visitors</td><td>Significant</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Competition</td><td>Low-Moderate</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Real Estate</td><td>Moderate-High ($20-30/sq ft)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Access</td><td>I-95, Route 1</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Local Regulations</h2>
      <p>Under <a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/rules" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Maine OCP regulations</a>, Scarborough operators must:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Obtain state license from Maine Office of Cannabis Policy</li>
        <li>Check local zoning for cannabis-friendly areas</li>
        <li>Meet all state compliance requirements</li>
        <li>Complete employee authorizations</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Best Locations</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Route 1</strong> - High traffic commercial corridor</li>
        <li><strong>Near Mall</li>
        <li><strong>Payless Plaza area</strong> - Shopping district</li>
        <li><strong>Gorham Road</strong> - Commercial zone</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Investment Requirements</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Category</th><th>Estimated Cost</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Real Estate (lease)</td><td>$3,500-6,000/mo</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Build-out</td><td>$100,000-180,000</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total <a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-costs/">Investment</a></td><td>$420,000-750,000</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="further-reading">
      <h2>Further Reading</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Office of Cannabis Policy (OCP)</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/rules" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Maine Cannabis Rules</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>This is for informational purposes only and does not constitute legal or financial advice. Consult with qualified professionals.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .further-reading { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .further-reading h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
</style>
